To fix the **‚Äúunauthenticated guest access‚Äù** issue shown in the screenshot, run this **one-liner** in an elevated PowerShell terminal on your **Windows 11** machine:

```powershell
Set-ItemProperty -Path "HKLM:\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services\LanmanWorkstation\Parameters" -Name AllowInsecureGuestAuth -Value 1 -Force
```

Then **restart your PC** or run:

```powershell
Restart-Computer
```

üí° This enables access to SMB shares that allow guest authentication (like some Proxmox shares). Be aware: it lowers security, so only use this in trusted local networks.
